\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Answer independence:\'a0
\f0\b0 Ads do not influence the answers ChatGPT gives you. Answers are optimized based on what's most helpful to you. Ads are always separate and clearly labeled.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cb2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Conversation privacy:\'a0
\f0\b0 We keep your conversations with ChatGPT private from advertisers, and we never sell your data to advertisers.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cb2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Choice and control:\'a0
\f0\b0 You control how your data is used. You can turn off personalization, and you can clear the data used for ads at any time. We\'92ll always offer a way to not see ads in ChatGPT, including a paid tier that\'92s ad-free.\cb1 \
